race.description: Girls Day Out On Sale Now Handicap (Bm70)
race.comment: A few of these bring great form to the race, none more so than REZONE (6). Made it two from two this prep when he finished too well at the end of 1400m at the Sunshine Coast last start. Ideally drawn and still gets in well after Williams' claim so the hat trick is alive. ECLAIR AWESOME (4) stepped up to the mile and ran a better race last time out at this track. Freshened up and with four wins from just nine starts she is certainly a mare worth following. DETRIMENTAL (3) and HEADHUNTER (5) clashed over this distance at Doomben two back and it was the latter who got home by a neck. Both are in outstanding form and should play a big role in the outcome.
